{"tid":1532180,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"九月係咪可以留係屋企涼冷氣瞓覺喇？","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:04:43.000Z","uid":69291,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"383d2bec578a9cccb0a3dea0b276e7688d18c17f","tid":1532180,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出面無人傾新行動咁滯<br />\n9月8係唔係遊行？？<br />\n幾時壓力測試？？？<br />\n再點改進？？？<br />\n係唔係要試下同法庭申請撤銷禁制令？？？<br />\n我地得返4-5日咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家我剩係見到個個講螢光粉同其他野<br />\n點樣再做壓力測試？幾時再做？<br />\n9月8日遊行極少文宣<br />\n我地就話知咩係香港人權民主法案啫<br />\n出面大把人未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人唔好再被代表喇好嘛<br />\n企出嚟, 自己同美國國會議員講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跪求文宣做圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請各位連登仔討論交通壓力測試<br />\n同向身邊人解釋香港人權民主法案<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>STAND WITH HONG KONG<br />\nFIGHT FOR FREEDOM</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"910d4514f039239550509c58ec58094c82834f10","tid":1532180,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"自己十連"},{"pid":"c1a85cc6d24